context.text: List of Asian American jurists - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
edia:Citing sources">sourced additions are welcome. This page is a list of Asian Americans . For more on who is considered Asian American, see Who is an Asian American? .

This is a list of Asian Americans who are or were judges , magistrate judges, court commissioners, or administrative law judges . In cases where a judge has served on multiple courts, the most recent court is listed.
For more on who is considered Asian American, see Who is an Asian American? .
